    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3088510/extras/195dbdcb19a047cd5dfc7f3ea4a60664.avif?t=1772173840\" width=1170 height=192 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Play as a <strong>fully-customisable magical die</strong>, equipped with unique spells on each of your faces that you cast with every step.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3088510/extras/7a8629b25d80c080586a36cacfaf1022.poster.avif?t=1772173840\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3088510/extras/7a8629b25d80c080586a36cacfaf1022.webm?t=1772173840\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3088510/extras/7a8629b25d80c080586a36cacfaf1022.mp4?t=1772173840\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Customise your die with the multitude of <strong>game-changing spells</strong> and upgrades you’ll discover as you roll along. Define<strong> your own unique build </strong>to face the obstacles in your path, perfecting your playstyle and putting it to the test.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3088510/extras/7e29409737826bec8e3a1e95e0f8d6bd.poster.avif?t=1772173840\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3088510/extras/7e29409737826bec8e3a1e95e0f8d6bd.webm?t=1772173840\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3088510/extras/7e29409737826bec8e3a1e95e0f8d6bd.mp4?t=1772173840\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3088510/extras/41fc49a036dc3a4cfa3909df48ed3e43.avif?t=1772173840\" width=1170 height=192 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Journey through <strong>a land of living game pieces</strong>, both friend and foe, to stand before the Gods of the Tabletop and reclaim that which has been discarded. Are you worthy of the grace of the gods? …Are they worthy of you?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3088510/extras/4f0e68a625c75cfe4fb900f1f211494e.poster.avif?t=1772173840\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3088510/extras/4f0e68a625c75cfe4fb900f1f211494e.webm?t=1772173840\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3088510/extras/4f0e68a625c75cfe4fb900f1f211494e.mp4?t=1772173840\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >From the fallen kingdom of the dominoes to the stacked streets of Casina City, all factions live <strong>uncertain lives</strong> under the whims of their arbitrary gods.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3088510/extras/9072eb6b3c76c0d1d42c7b2c6366e0f7.poster.avif?t=1772173840\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3088510/extras/9072eb6b3c76c0d1d42c7b2c6366e0f7.webm?t=1772173840\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3088510/extras/9072eb6b3c76c0d1d42c7b2c6366e0f7.mp4?t=1772173840\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3088510/extras/827a8a08d4164cd1f9ef7efe6082d1d3.avif?t=1772173840\" width=1170 height=192 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Each new spell, enemy, and obstacle you encounter adds a <strong>new layer of complexity</strong> to the dice-builder game system for you to manipulate.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3088510/extras/7eeb6d28894ecadff7eeaab74f5b38ef.poster.avif?t=1772173840\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3088510/extras/7eeb6d28894ecadff7eeaab74f5b38ef.webm?t=1772173840\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3088510/extras/7eeb6d28894ecadff7eeaab74f5b38ef.mp4?t=1772173840\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Awaken the obelisks hidden in the corners of this world to challenge yourself with <strong>focused challenges</strong> to perfect every part of your mastery of the die.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3088510/extras/8394a01f9b431a23b51e20023a4de18f.poster.avif?t=1772173840\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3088510/extras/8394a01f9b431a23b51e20023a4de18f.webm?t=1772173840\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3088510/extras/8394a01f9b431a23b51e20023a4de18f.mp4?t=1772173840\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Compete with other players to find the most efficient solutions to the challenges on our playtest, with a <strong>new challenge dropping every fortnight!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3088510/extras/06b37d4dd9db87b81c8719e6ca4fcdaf.avif?t=1772173840\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3088510/extras_big/06b37d4dd9db87b81c8719e6ca4fcdaf.avif?t=1772173840 width=1560 height=878 /></span></p>",
